divs: Sighting DetailsIt was there long enough for me to run and get my camera and I took two clicks and after that is was gone. You can actually see it moving so fast that in the pictures it shows the thing at three differnt spots in each picture. I am a sky watcher and have been since a child Nebraska is a good place to find them expecailly in the country on a nice clear night. My mom has been a sky watcher since she was 15 and I know the differnce between a plain or a military air carft and this is the first time that my mother or I have been able to catch it on camera.
